message: Failed at least one business validation rules

errors.description: [IRASC5-016]-If the Invoice currency code (IBT-005) is not 'SGD', the Invoice MUST have exactly one Additional Supporting Document as follows: Document type code (BT-SG-002) MUST be 'sgdtotal-incl-gst', Supporting document description MUST be provided, Invoiced object identifier MUST be 'SGD'.
[IRASC5-101]-The Total amount including GST in SGD, if provided, MUST be numeric and have no more than 2 decimals.
